.TH GET_SERIAL_NUMBER_6022 1 "April 2026" "hantek6022api 2.10.9" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
get_serial_number_6022 \- get serial number from Hantek 6022BE/BL oscilloscope
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B get_serial_number_6022
[\fB\-h\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Read and print the unique serial number from a Hantek 6022BE/BL USB oscilloscope.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Show help message and exit.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR calibrate_6022 (1),
.BR capture_6022 (1),
.BR upload_firmware_6022 (1)
